Amazon Price Monitor

Dependencies: BeautifulSoup4, lxml (parser), Requests, Python 2.7

	$ pip install beautifulsoup4
	$ pip install requests
	$ pip install lxml

If pip installation fails: 
	$ curl https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py | python

After installing dependencies, run scrapper.py:

	$ python scrapper.py

Use different amazon urls for monitoring different products in scrapper.py
